description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Lead Paediatric Diabetic Nurse Specialist/s to join the children&#39;s diabetes team at Salisbury NHS Foundation Trust. We are looking for an enthusiastic and motivated nurse/s to join the committed multidisciplinary paediatric diabetes team. This is a challenging, fulfilling and exciting post .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working in partnership with a small but enthusiastic multi-disciplinary team, this role will be key in shaping the future of the service, ensuring that it continues to meet the needs of children and young people living with diabetes, as set out in the Paediatric Diabetes Best Practice Tariff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our multi-disciplinary diabetes team provides a comprehensive diabetes service for children and young people. The successful applicant/s would be leading and coordinating the care for children and young people with diabetes and their families in a variety of settings including: hospital, home and school. They would be providing essential assessment, on-going care and support as well as creating and delivering educational programs, both for children &amp; young people, their families and a wide variety of professionals working in various settings (schools, nurseries, hospital wards, etc).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With close support from the multidisciplinary team (Paediatric consultants, psychologist, paediatric diabetes nurses and specialist dietician), the post holder/s will have the opportunity to build upon their existing knowledge and skills, and further develop their own nursing practice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At least 2 years paediatric diabetes experience is essential and previous line management experience would be advantageous, although the successful candidate will be fully supported in developing their leadership skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to the hours available for this position, we are looking to recruit 2 x post-holders and will consider full or part-time applications&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ruth Radley, Head of Nursing &amp; Trust Lead for Care of Children on email r.radley@nhs.net.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Ruth Radley&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title Head of Nursing &amp; Trust Lead for Care of Children&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address r.radley@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 07876 251739&lt;/p&gt;
